{"tid":2092211,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"魯比奧將提案禁華企進美市場","createTime":"2020-07-03T06:01:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T06:27:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a985279c83ce69a633f8cf7042cbad94293e7eca","tid":2092211,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/YVK5VYI35EGXHB7DRS35ABI6BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FYVK5VYI35EGXHB7DRS35ABI6BA%2F&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXIT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=9e746f47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200703%2FYVK5VYI35EGXHB7DRS35ABI6BA%2F&h=0bbe6547\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200703/YVK5VYI35EGXHB7DRS35ABI6BA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n魯比奧將提案禁華企進美市場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/I_KncJIGGykjQdkcNGIp_z_Ro_U=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QPNPMLVK3F666HAZXOD6A7JEDM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FI_KncJIGGykjQdkcNGIp_z_Ro_U%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQPNPMLVK3F666HAZXOD6A7JEDM.jpg&h=80014523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國參議員魯比奧為《香港人權與民主法案》重要推動者。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港版國安法實施後，中美緊張關係仍僵持不下，美方擬向中國「出招」，採取金融制裁行動。《香港人權與民主法案》推手之一、美國參議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio）周四表示，計劃未來數周提出禁止中國企業進入美國資本市場法案。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：傳媒隨時中招 譚耀宗：明眼人識分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n針對間諜及侵犯人權者<br />\n<br />\n對華立場鷹派的魯比奧，昨日發聲明指將計劃立法禁止中國企業進入美國資本市場，主要針對從事間諜活動、侵犯人權<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n動重要反華措施，例如立法制裁曾鎮壓新疆維吾爾族的中國官員。"},{"pid":"93845f4ed247fc02326b7336fcc4ea3c763b5c72","tid":2092211,"uid":231908,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:03:12.000Z","msg":"如果共和黨佢出而唔係大豆侵咪幾好，可惜4年前被KO<br />\n不過仲後生，希望4年後再戰"},{"pid":"5cba97b8000b205326fce143d37199f4ad17d32f","tid":2092211,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"希望侵侵爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c7c86688b5da942255146f75f2bc84f7121bd6","tid":2092211,"uid":190333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93845f4ed247fc02326b7336fcc4ea3c763b5c72","tid":2092211,"uid":231908,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:03:12.000Z","msg":"如果共和黨佢出而唔係大豆侵咪幾好，可惜4年前被KO<br />\n不過仲後生，希望4年後再戰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:07:05.000Z","msg":"佢同ted cruz都係<br />\nRubio仲要畀大豆侵笑係古巴人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb66647a30e3ae768074cfae095e262f80aa2f1","tid":2092211,"uid":5128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29c7c86688b5da942255146f75f2bc84f7121bd6","tid":2092211,"uid":190333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93845f4ed247fc02326b7336fcc4ea3c763b5c72","tid":2092211,"uid":231908,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:03:12.000Z","msg":"如果共和黨佢出而唔係大豆侵咪幾好，可惜4年前被KO<br />\n不過仲後生，希望4年後再戰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:07:05.000Z","msg":"佢同ted cruz都係<br />\nRubio仲要畀大豆侵笑係古巴人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"古巴人比人極權統治<br />\n根本人地就知有幾慘 <br />\n錢無左可以搵 <br />\n人經歷係一生"},{"pid":"0510a8d05f3bd1feae9ba3775d34c3cfc3335bdc","tid":2092211,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cba97b8000b205326fce143d37199f4ad17d32f","tid":2092211,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"希望侵侵爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T06:11:29.000Z","m